data.description: Don't miss this stunning home, just minutes away from Fort Carson! This conveniently located 3 bedroom cutie has had a complete makeover with new paint inside and out, new roof, brand new carpet, LVP flooring, and granite countertops. The bathroom has been completely remodeled. The kitchen offers new cabinets, granite counters, and all new stainless steel appliances.  You might even like doing laundry in the giant laundry room!  Natural light streams in from all over the home. Quick access to shopping, food and entertainment...look no further! This home has it all!
